HOW IT'S MADE
-------------

- Install Dart, or download Dart SDK archive (it can be used without installation).

- To check the version:

    > dart info

- If required, edit "DartWorker.dart".

- Run

    > build.cmd

    It will create "dartworker.exe".

- Run "testXXX.cmd" to perform simple tests.

- Commit the changes (including "dartworker.exe").
